{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Pizzapocalypse is a short game made by eighteen Year 2 students, in around twelve weeks of dedicated development.</strong> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>The Story</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It feels like the world has forgotten about the joys of authentic, handmade pizza since the oppressive Pizza Corps moved into town with their &quot;cheap and efficient&quot; pizza-in-a-can... but one pizza chef is determined to deliver rich, traditional Italian cuisine. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224960/extras/6gifnew.gif?t=1731620845\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pizzapocalypse is a cartoony 3D platformer for all skill levels! As a chef, use your pizza to dash and bounce your way across rooftops, and fight robot minions as you traverse a corporation-ridden town to make a delivery to your loyal customers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take your time exploring every corner of the beautiful town, and collecting toppings to get the highest score possible!<i> Or</i> master your toolkit to get the fastest time, and attempt to complete bonus challenges. All play styles and skill levels can enjoy Pizzapocalypse!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game takes place in one level. Explore the three beautiful and distinct areas, each with multiple paths to uncover, and their own unique gameplay challenges and aesthetic!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Made with love!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3224960/539f863c46ba1cc984f4f3506baeb5e91c403967.jpg"},{"name":"Keep the tip!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3224960/e35b336c74d4966f8f37565361cab3a9f2cce063.jpg"},{"name":"Every bit counts","path":"https://cdn.akamai.s